{"tid":327354,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人同我一樣有飛行恐懼症","createTime":"2017-07-18T16:39:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-22T19:20:02.000Z","uid":119027,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"12c462eff77bce063c73cfb12246fc1d720d4976","tid":327354,"uid":119027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:39:03.000Z","msg":"由細到大都唔太鍾意搭飛機<br />\n唔鍾意嗰種困喺個鐵盒入面被迫離地既感覺<br />\n不過細個最多都係起飛同有氣流既時候可能有少少緊張<br />\n但係呢一兩年搭過幾次飛機<br />\n一次降落嗰陣勁大氣流好似過山車咁<br />\n一次起飛嗰時又係氣流搞到半個鐘都仲係升唔到上去正常高度<br />\n一次就降落嗰陣唔知最乜要來回幾次先落到地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自從呢幾次之後我每次諗起搭飛機都會好緊張，完全打消晒所有去旅行既念頭<br />\n<br />\n問題就係公司無啦啦要我下星期飛一轉大陸做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搭中國的飛機仲要呢幾日啲天氣咁唔穩定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我怕我未遇到空難已經會喺飛機上面窒息死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有無巴打有同樣問題可以介紹鎮定劑比我上機食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd7a1393555944cdb0b9b105e87688d0d8281b45","tid":327354,"uid":3914,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:42:04.000Z","msg":"會成日亂諗自己會出事<br />\n又怕自己真係出左事屋企人點算<br />\n搵唔到條屍又比個假希望佢地好殘忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8e7639e16e318cb9c1e61ca2f2b1a98d54627a7","tid":327354,"uid":27831,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:59:03.000Z","msg":"手心每次都濕晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽到引擎大聲變細聲個陣<br />\n我以為佢個引擎停撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6ef41611fb74f4b4c27bb6a2e92d0de9c3273c7","tid":327354,"uid":119027,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T17:23:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會成日亂諗自己會出事<br />\n又怕自己真係出左事屋企人點算<br />\n搵唔到條屍又比個假希望佢地好殘忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n成日話咩飛機失事既機率好低<br />\n但係呢排見真係好多事故<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最慘係飛機失事真係無得走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n飛到咁高跌落去都要咁上下時間先到地<br />\n諗起嗰段時間既絕望真係好得人驚"},{"pid":"ed0d4d15b8812a731f8b25173c21d8c8f2bc5aed","tid":327354,"uid":36575,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T17:27:54.000Z","msg":"我有錢 但我都好驚"},{"pid":"0f91b195c6171e5dd5c713b9b957e939ff9a1445","tid":327354,"uid":13724,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T17:56:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>由細到大都唔太鍾意搭飛機<br />\n唔鍾意嗰種困喺個鐵盒入面被迫離地既感覺<br />\n不過細個最多都係起飛同有氣流既時候可能有少少緊張<br />\n但係呢一兩年搭過幾次飛機<br />\n一次降落嗰陣勁大氣流好似過山車咁<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">一次起飛嗰時又係氣流搞到半個鐘都仲係升唔到上去正常高度</span><br />\n一次就降落嗰陣唔知最乜要來回幾次先落到地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自從呢幾次之後我每次諗起搭飛機都會好緊張，完全打消晒所有去旅行既念頭<br />\n<br />\n問題就係公司無啦啦要我下星期飛一轉大陸做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搭中國的飛機仲要呢幾日啲天氣咁唔穩定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我怕我未遇到空難已經會喺飛機上面窒息死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有無巴打有同樣問題可以介紹鎮定劑比我上機食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n紅字不嬲上去都要半個鐘㗎啦，關氣流乜事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e716fc589a6843971ed52b2aa7df76dd584d933f","tid":327354,"uid":17777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T17:56:50.000Z","msg":"本身都有啲焦慮，仲要係外國讀書，諗到坐飛機都驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f8e935bd40ca53bba1362ef3e80a5caadecaa79","tid":327354,"uid":119027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T18:03:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>由細到大都唔太鍾意搭飛機<br />\n唔鍾意嗰種困喺個鐵盒入面被迫離地既感覺<br />\n不過細個最多都係起飛同有氣流既時候可能有少少緊張<br />\n但係呢一兩年搭過幾次飛機<br />\n一次降落嗰陣勁大氣流好似過山車咁<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">一次起飛嗰時又係氣流搞到半個鐘都仲係升唔到上去正常高度</span><br />\n一次就降落嗰陣唔知最乜要來回幾次先落到地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自從呢幾次之後我每次諗起搭飛機都會好緊張，完全打消晒所有去旅行既念頭<br />\n<br />\n問題就係公司無啦啦要我下星期飛一轉大陸做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搭中國的飛機仲要呢幾日啲天氣咁唔穩定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我怕我未遇到空難已經會喺飛機上面窒息死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有無巴打有同樣問題可以介紹鎮定劑比我上機食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n紅字不嬲上去都要半個鐘㗎啦，關氣流乜事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係喎我係feel到架機唔係直線向上<br />\n仲要有幾下急墜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fd4105016403ed73eb7b473d41e77269d0ef047","tid":327354,"uid":119027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T18:05:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本身都有啲焦慮，仲要係外國讀書，諗到坐飛機都驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我之前都係外國讀者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連埋轉機十七個鐘都可以安安樂樂咁瞓覺<br />\n究竟係天氣差左定係我越大越細膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2acacc811456c085e83d583c64e95d41234d82a","tid":327354,"uid":13724,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T18:32:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>由細到大都唔太鍾意搭飛機<br />\n唔鍾意嗰種困喺個鐵盒入面被迫離地既感覺<br />\n不過細個最多都係起飛同有氣流既時候可能有少少緊張<br />\n但係呢一兩年搭過幾次飛機<br />\n一次降落嗰陣勁大氣流好似過山車咁<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">一次起飛嗰時又係氣流搞到半個鐘都仲係升唔到上去正常高度</span><br />\n一次就降落嗰陣唔知最乜要來回幾次先落到地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自從呢幾次之後我每次諗起搭飛機都會好緊張，完全打消晒所有去旅行既念頭<br />\n<br />\n問題就係公司無啦啦要我下星期飛一轉大陸做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搭中國的飛機仲要呢幾日啲天氣咁唔穩定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我怕我未遇到空難已經會喺飛機上面窒息死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有無巴打有同樣問題可以介紹鎮定劑比我上機食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n紅字不嬲上去都要半個鐘㗎啦，關氣流乜事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係喎我係feel到架機唔係直線向上<br />\n仲要有幾下急墜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n飛機呀，火箭咩？直線向上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"446942cad2d99e495a05d607b2465815e32e5505","tid":327354,"uid":99582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T19:57:46.000Z","msg":"帶安眠藥上機食"},{"pid":"1058326dadc201a7d80753f0afdcb9dfe2725154","tid":327354,"uid":82542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T20:53:46.000Z","msg":"我搭飛機個耳仔會好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9763475d4295ca101ffa8c7d57fe87547f9c2b3","tid":327354,"uid":128127,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T21:08:35.000Z","msg":"係我 成日坐飛機果陣驚失事 雖然明知空難仲難過中六合彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每次搭飛機果十幾廿粒鐘我都全程勁不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa37b363246a0dad17deb55c5e2b220d4b9e07fe","tid":327354,"uid":89287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T21:31:04.000Z","msg":"以前都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家搭到麻木左"},{"pid":"371dd46628bb280ac6598b3f193826ede967b974","tid":327354,"uid":47674,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T21:48:55.000Z","msg":"上機前一晚會睇 Air Crash Investigation <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f2bd7c357820550879f6aefab3c631cc7454916","tid":327354,"uid":70092,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T22:07:21.000Z","msg":"以前同你一樣，其實依家都 dd驚<br />\n上面講果 d咩訓教/做其他野實定唔得<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係驚搭飛機既人係唔會做到以上既野<br />\n由上機驚到落機<br />\n我既解決方法係：<br />\n1 唔好坐廉航，坐大間 d既，之後你上網睇多 d間 airline既資料，拎乜乜7獎，安全系數係幾高咁，睇多 d關菸飛機安全既資料<br />\n你上機就諗住呢 d野，你會安心好多，同埋正常 airline有野食下有野飲下會安心好多<br />\n2 連續坐多幾次飛機，真係連續可能係兩三個月飛4 5次，真係會慣會好好多"},{"pid":"b422aa3f3600a8d3e597a529923422d1c5171336","tid":327354,"uid":65568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T22:11:59.000Z","msg":"每次坐飛機一有氣流就好撚驚 <br />\n一定要捉住啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過太鐘意去旅行 <br />\n驚都要撘"},{"pid":"380e864c9be4d7adb66965771e54144d176479ba","tid":327354,"uid":66779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T22:17:52.000Z","msg":"睇死神來了5 睇多幾次麻木咗就甚麼鬼也不怕"},{"pid":"3f4647178e4e500a6044f6d6830be490c28b508a","tid":327354,"uid":105888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T22:22:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每次坐飛機一有氣流就好撚驚 <br />\n一定要捉住啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過太鐘意去旅行 <br />\n驚都要撘</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nsame <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外每次落機耳仔都勁撚痛<br />\n打喊露/擘大口/ 食香口膠都冇用<br />\n<br />\n係咪 eustachian tube太細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽日仲要skydive<br />\n唔知急速落14000尺耳仔點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d24415f7b82c14dbe5fa2218b74abcde286e34de