7,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T17:28:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我有呀！！！！<br />\n終於搵到同伴啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我一直覺得自己有病<br />\n之後經歷過一次搭飛機有氣流<br />\n同玩過山車全程無叫屈左係個心到之後<br />\n我從此唔敢搭飛機同埋好驚<br />\n每次逼住要搭個時都要食藥<br />\n一有小小氣流就好緊張 <br />\n會有d 透唔到氣既感覺 唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有無藥介紹？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0016763b2a12a6d54bdb3fa3b1e839ca3e30855e","tid":327354,"uid":30396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T17:30:06.000Z","msg":"巴打我終於搵到知音喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n細個同屋企人去完一次旅行試過一程機有4次氣流<br />\n仲要係急降左幾次個隻之後，就一直都係驚搭飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到一直唔敢去得遠，黎黎去去都係台灣個Ｄ，最遠都係泰國咋屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad9a16cf43a522e59c0bb840254993092556ad43","tid":327354,"uid":119027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T17:35:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實搭飛機好安全架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算有氣流架搞到飛機好似過山車咁，對於個結構黎講其實係好小事<br />\n雖然我都明白呢啲係心理上覺得驚，唔係咁容易克服到。。。<br />\n我係有份設計飛機引擎既工程師，如果有問題我可以嘗試解答下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我想知飛機失速既機會率有幾大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔驚佢會散開<br />\n但係我成日形住喺氣流入面chok下chok下架飛機會突然無左動力然後就失控向下跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw 巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果我個問題太on9唔好笑我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"092671dc2590800aed35759435bdc6afb04b1a35","tid":327354,"uid":119027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T17:39:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打我終於搵到知音喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n細個同屋企人去完一次旅行試過一程機有4次氣流<br />\n仲要係急降左幾次個隻之後，就一直都係驚搭飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到一直唔敢去得遠，黎黎去去都係台灣個Ｄ，最遠都係泰國咋屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都試過番香港遇著八號風球被迫轉去台灣<br />\n不過台灣降落天氣都唔好勁多氣流<br />\n落到地全機人鼓掌多謝機師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係始終細個都係唔係好識驚<br />\n大個左唔知係咪細膽左好容易有陰影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"832a7b4891a0173e9e38bc70b88c29f6668d088f","tid":327354,"uid":43964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T17:43:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.turbulenceforecast.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.turbulenceforecast.com%2F&d=4IccKxcDMBkg%2FQisIQ2xTf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=8a808119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.turbulenceforecast.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n自己飛前睇forecast,有積雨雲既地方就有機會有氣流，CAT 晴空氣流，即係無雲既氣流，多數係jet stream 附近形成。"},{"pid":"1b0de772a190211d76deae5ff8ed0c97f3f140f8","tid":327354,"uid":128127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T18:43:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PodBIfQ2ALQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DPodBIfQ2ALQ&d=4IccKxcDMBkg%2FQisIQ2xTf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=3be0fb26\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PodBIfQ2ALQ</a><br />\n樓主睇完呢條片應該會安心d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想當年細個第一次喺電視睇呢套戲<br />\n睇完第二日搭飛機去加拿大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一打開個窗坐正機翼位望到隻機殘殘舊舊<br />\n準備起飛既時候仲要搖搖下就嚟甩咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過細個真係無咁大反應<br />\n反而我呀媽嗰程機嚇到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n加拿大撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最驚搭飛內陸d小型飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb783d9eebcd17b80530a08442f169f29e9d90f2","tid":327354,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T21:36:28.000Z","msg":"焦慮症 唔敢搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c0b2d1a297f2ab3a30c204b213cc3a14f23bbf7","tid":327354,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T21:36:45.000Z","msg":"焦慮症 唔敢搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b8daaae962ef848f35f5f7e1a57751ce5f72d41","tid":327354,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T21:37:03.000Z","msg":"焦慮症 唔敢搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df9a86ed63ce367a76e6e3a3dcc3b8b9bf675d66","tid":327354,"uid":119027,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T07:31:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>焦慮症 唔敢搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇得出巴打真係好焦慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b4d3b39232ff1cba0195f0b7cb11f169a29564c","tid":327354,"uid":73804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T13:19:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實搭飛機好安全架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算有氣流架搞到飛機好似過山車咁，對於個結構黎講其實係好小事<br />\n雖然我都明白呢啲係心理上覺得驚，唔係咁容易克服到。。。<br />\n我係有份設計飛機引擎既工程師，如果有問題我可以嘗試解答下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我想知飛機失速既機會率有幾大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔驚佢會散開<br />\n但係我成日形住喺氣流入面chok下chok下架飛機會突然無左動力然後就失控向下跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw 巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果我個問題太on9唔好笑我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n失速喺由於飛機既angle of attack過大而發生。就算飛機突然冇咗動力，架飛機都唔會即刻跌落黎，而係會繼續滑翔。<br />\n而家既飛機引擎係好可靠，好少會有failure 。就算真係有engine failure，大型客機有最少兩個引擎。同埋飛機師都有定期既訓練去應付呢啲情況。所以唔需要擔心架"},{"pid":"0bfc910d9a13716191816d59b7bca162362d3ce8","tid":327354,"uid":73804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T13:34:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實搭飛機好安全架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算有氣流架搞到飛機好似過山車咁，對於個結構黎講其實係好小事<br />\n雖然我都明白呢啲係心理上覺得驚，唔係咁容易克服到。。。<br />\n我係有份設計飛機引擎既工程師，如果有問題我可以嘗試解答下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解有時飛到中段個引擎會突然靜哂？ 每次都會遇到哩個位好驚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我諗係飛機下降嗰陣先會咁樣？因為飛機師係會靠調整引擎既動力去控制下降既速度。如果你聽到靜晒，好可能個引擎係空轉(idle)緊，而唔係熄咗。等於你揸車落緊斜嗰陣唔會繼續比油。"}]}